metadata.name: Kichijoten (吉祥天)
metadata.description:
Japanese goddess of beauty and fertility, worshiped primarily by women.   

She's the Japanese Buddhism's version of the Indian goddess Lakshmi. She grants beauty, fertility and happiness to her worshipers, and is sometimes included as one of the Seven Lucky Gods. 

Artwork created with Midjourney (Ai) + Bazaart + Adobe Lightroom Photoshop
